view.name: AH Cumulative Provisional COVID-19 Deaths by Sex, Race, and Age from 1/1/2020 to 7/28/2020
view.description: Cumulative provisional counts of deaths sex, race/Hispanic origin, age group, and by select underlying causes of death.  The dataset also includes provisional counts of death for COVID-19, coded to ICD-10 code U07.1 as an underlying or multiple cause of death.  Includes deaths that occurred between January 1, 2020 to July 28, 2020.
